==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: antineutron
<hw>antineutron</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The antiparticle of a neutron.
It has the same mass as a neutron, but a spin and magnetic moment
opposite that of the neutron.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Antinomian</ent>⟦br⟧
